<div class="oracle-header">
<h3 id="toc8"><span>FROM THE DESK OF ORACLE</span></h3>
<hr />
<p>The Centre received a distress signal on 9 August, one week after losing contact with MFT CHARYBDIS. The signal lacked exact co-ordinates but contained an audio file.</p>
<p>The audio file, as relayed by Giant Radio Squid (<em>107.9 Calamari FM</em>), is as follows.</p>
</div>
<div class="oracle-header" style="text-align: left;">
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>[BEGIN LOG]</strong></p>
<hr />
<p><strong>First Avian Entity:</strong> If you're willing to comply, let's–</p>
<p><strong>C-1 Quinn:</strong> Where are your owners?</p>
<p><strong>First Avian Entity:</strong> What?</p>
<p><strong>C-1 Quinn:</strong> Oh, you know. Humans!</p>
<p><strong>First Avian Entity:</strong> What do you mean? We don't <em>have</em> humans, what are you–</p>
<p><strong>Second Avian Entity:</strong> Quibba, I know what he means. Why don't I tell him what's going on? He might be a fiend–</p>
<p><strong>C-1 Quinn:</strong> <em>Hey!</em></p>
<p><strong>Second Avian Entity:</strong> &#8212; But given the circumstances, even <em>he</em> could help us.</p>
<p><strong>First Avian Entity:</strong> Fine.</p>
<p><strong>Second Avian Entity:</strong> Some months ago, humanity faced a daring threat and found themselves most unequipped to combat it. Their threat, an innocent memetic agent, proved insidious over time and affected large swaths of their population to no end.</p>
<p><strong>Second Avian Entity:</strong> That simple hazard turned into a worldwide pandemic. Young parents started feeding worms to their kin. Human language was abolished and replaced with calls and songs. Entire populations migrated hundreds of kilometres south, never to return home. I think some humans even tried flying; you can imagine how that went. These are but a few examples of humanity's vast struggle &#8212; one that consumed their entire species.</p>
<p><strong>Second Avian Entity:</strong> It was as if one unruly God discarded all that defines humanity and tried to fit something primitive &#8212; something bird-like &#8212; into that gaping hole. Suffering came in waves, and because civilization is suited for humankind and not bird-kind, all societal norms quickly deteriorated. Humanity ceased to be, and even the mighty Foundation fell to its knees. There is no longer such a thing as human.</p>
<p><strong>Second Avian Entity:</strong> My team and I operate in one of the only minute pockets of normalcy that still exists, alongside a few other untainted resources. It is arduous work, but it is our duty. And I fear our hardships have only just begun.</p>
<p><strong>C-1 Quinn:</strong> I don't get it.</p>
<p><strong>Second Avian Entity:</strong> You could never hope to. Speaking of which, who are you? We did not detect the proto-Avian meme complex within you. Only an experienced thaumaturge &#8212; perhaps even a powerful Type-Green, Medila forbid! &#8212; could resist such a memetic threat. Tell me: What manipulation has Thoth attempted this time?</p>
<p><strong>C-1 Quinn:</strong> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[</span><em>He laughs.</em><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">]</span> Oh, we're just visiting. My team is part of something called the Centre. We–</p>
<p><strong>First Avian Entity:</strong> The Centre? Are you those shark-punching–</p>
<p><strong>C-1 Quinn:</strong> Come on! How many times must a man explain himself? It's Selachian Pugilism!</p>
<p><strong>First Avian Entity:</strong> Do not interrupt me again. Explain how you will pay for your crimes, thaumaturge!</p>
<p><strong>C-1 Quinn:</strong> Listen, I'm no wizard. I'm a Pugilist. And what do you mean by <em>crimes</em>? Are you telling me we <em>didn't</em> pound that Deviant to pulp? We saved the city!</p>
<p><strong>Second Avian Entity:</strong> Quibba makes a good point. Cease your nonsense, or I will be a very cross bird. Are you willing to co-operate?</p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[</span><em>Pause.</em><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">]</span></p>
<p><strong>C-1 Quinn:</strong> Actually yeah, I am. What did you say you were, again? Pelican birds?</p>
<p><strong>Second Avian Entity:</strong> We are members of the Avian Division's Mobile Task Force Eta-4, code-named “Begone Thoth”. I am Keshrayuth, leader of this unit.</p>
<p><strong>C-1 Quinn:</strong> Right, about that. Where I'm from, we used birds<sup><strong>[A]</strong></sup> like you to fight Selachians. If you're willing to supply some muscle for our war, we're gonna help you fight yours. Full co-operation on both sides. Deal?</p>
<p><strong>Second Avian Entity:</strong> Deal.</p>
<hr />
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>[END LOG]</strong></p>
<hr />
<p><strong>[A]</strong> This is a reference to “GALLINACEOUS STRIFE”: A two-phase project developed by the proto-Centre organization “Union of American States' Center for Institutionalized Impacting” (UASCII). Because some Avian phenotypes are natural predators of the common Selachian, GALLINACEOUS STRIFE used Avian entities to neutralize Selachian threats.</p>
<p><strong>Phase One:</strong> Phase one used Deviant-Type Avian entities, like the “LIMP FIREBIRD”, to engage in the sport of cockfighting with Selachian entities. Phase one was dissolved after an extensive investigation into the project's unlawful and unethical violation of Avian rights.</p>
<p><strong>Phase Two:</strong> Phase two involved the creation of a dense Avian meme complex (code-named “GAUSS KESTREL”) to neutralize Deviant-Type Selachian entities. Because no actual Avian entities were being manipulated, no Avian rights could be violated. GAUSS KESTREL was dissolved when the Avian meme complex was lost to unknown Extra-Universal forces.</p>
<p>GALLINACEOUS STRIFE remains ON HIATUS to this day.</p>
</div>
<div class="oracle-header">
<p><strong>Tail-End:</strong> No further transmissions on the current whereabouts of MFT CHARYBDIS have been received.</p>
<p>CICAPOCO is calling on all its resources to form a new Marine Fighting Team for SPC-507.</p>
</div>
